        <summary>サービスが指定された仮想パスでアクティブ化されることを保証します。</summary>
        <remarks>
          <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## 解説  
 This method is used by third\-party transport developers to activate the service at the provided virtual path if that service is not already active. This method is idempotent so that once it has been called, calling it again with the same **parameterReference tag is not supported!!!!**  
 specified is safe in the sense that it has no effect.  
  
 The expected virtual path format is `/<app-name>/<sub-directory/<service-name>.svc` or `~/<sub-directory/<service-name>.svc` where `<app-name>` is the application name,  `<sub-directory>` is the IIS virtual directory, and `<service-name>` is the service name.  
  
   
  
## 例  
 ]]></format>
        </remarks>
